Joint Programming-initiative Neurodegenerative Disease Research (JPND) is a research initiative aimed at tackling the challenge of neurodegenerative diseases. JPND aims to increase coordinated investment between participating countries in research aimed at finding causes, developing cures, and identifying appropriate ways to care for those with neurodegenerative diseases. This is a call for multi-national research projects on health social care for neurodegenerative diseases.

  "en": "Joint Programming-initiative Neurodegenerative Disease Research (JPND) is a research initiative aimed at tackling the challenge of neurodegenerative diseases. JPND aims to increase coordinated investment between participating countries in research aimed at finding causes, developing cures, and identifying appropriate ways to care for those with neurodegenerative diseases. This is a call for multi-national research projects on health social care for neurodegenerative diseases."
